inux-plumbers-talk/","depth":2},{"title":"Speech Script for OSDI 2025 bpftime talk \"Extending Applications Safely and Efficiently\"","href":"/others/miscellaneous/osdi-talk/","depth":2},{"title":"bpftime roadmap and ideas for 2024","href":"/others/miscellaneous/roadmap/","depth":2},{"title":"eBPF Summit 2025 bpftime talk","href":"/others/miscellaneous/talk-ebpf-summit/","depth":2},{"title":"Securing and Simplifying eBPF Deployments with WebAssembly","href":"/others/miscellaneous/wasm-bpf-kubecon/","depth":2},{"title":"talk draft in kubecon","href":"/others/miscellaneous/wasm-bpf-talk/","depth":2},{"title":"NVBit 内部机制深度分析","href":"/others/nvbit-tutorial/nvbit-internals/","depth":2},{"title":"NVBit Tutorial: Comprehensive Guide to GPU Binary Instrumentation","href":"/others/nvbit-tutorial/","depth":1},{"title":"NVBit Tutorial: Basic Block Instruction Counting","href":"/others/nvbit-tutorial/tools/instr_count_bb/","depth":3},{"title":"NVBit Tutorial: Instruction Counting with CUDA Graphs Support","href":"/others/nvbit-tutorial/tools/instr_count_cuda_graph/","depth":3},{"title":"NVBit Tutorial: Instruction Counting","href":"/others/nvbit-tutorial/tools/instr_count/","depth":3},{"title":"NVBit Tutorial: GPU-to-CPU Printing with memprintf2","href":"/others/nvbit-tutorial/tools/mem_printf2/","depth":3},{"title":"NVBit Tutorial: Memory Tracing","href":"/others/nvbit-tutorial/tools/mem_trace/","depth":3},{"title":"NVBit Tutorial: MOV Instruction Replacement","href":"/others/nvbit-tutorial/tools/mov_replace/","depth":3},{"title":"NVBit Tutorial: Opcode Histogram","href":"/others/nvbit-tutorial/tools/opcode_hist/","depth":3},{"title":"NVBit Tutorial Tools","href":"/others/nvbit-tutorial/tools/","depth":2},{"title":"NVBit Tutorial: Register Value Recording","href":"/others/nvbit-tutorial/tools/record_reg_vals/","depth":3},{"title":"ebpf usecases analysis","href":"/others/usecases/","depth":1}]}]}},"__N_SSG":true}